# Cloudflare Pages: the Vite build renames index.html -> dashboard.html, so the
# bare "/" has no index and 404s. Redirect only the root to the clean /dashboard
# URL (which CF serves from dashboard.html).
#
# NOTE: do NOT use a "/*  /dashboard.html  200" catch-all here — CF Pages
# auto-redirects /dashboard.html -> /dashboard (308), so a catch-all rewrite to
# /dashboard.html creates an infinite redirect loop (ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS).
/    /dashboard    302
